  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/567a94fd05a1275516c99bcdb6deb3b8.webp?t=1732119247\" width=32 height=32 /></span><br><br>\"The Enemy Weapons Are Better\" is a simple, fast-paced barrage game.<br><br>A bunch of red creatures with a spirit of defiance invade the data world. And CANO is going to beat them. But<br>CANO has no arms, or magic. Therefore, he needs to use his feet to run and guide the enemy's weapons to kill the enemy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Understanding attack methods</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/40640b369fafb682c70d7e91116af4c0.poster.avif?t=1732119247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/40640b369fafb682c70d7e91116af4c0.webm?t=1732119247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/40640b369fafb682c70d7e91116af4c0.mp4?t=1732119247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Move, guide weapons to hit enemies, but be careful, while also dealing damage to the player.<br><br>KILL 8 bosses, then you can use their weapons to clean up the remaining forces.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features</h2><br>-Can be archived at any time.<br>-The operation is simple, just move and mouse click to upgrade.<br>-Relatively good sense of blow.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >operating instructions</h2><br>-WASD moves, left mouse button to purchase upgrades.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In addition</h2><br>- Join discord: ",
